{"tid":1484522,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"得罪講句","createTime":"2019-08-18T14:48:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T15:58:00.000Z","uid":17024,"like":33,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"d01815ef02b61d4678bd7582d6234f552b4834bc","tid":1484522,"uid":17024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:48:23.000Z","msg":"今日金鐘比人捉嘅人<br />\n係抵死<br />\n講到明速龍圍緊，政總大批狗<br />\n170 萬人嘅努力<br />\n會被白白浪費<br />\n<br />\n你要勇武送頭唔急在一時<br />\n今日送頭搏唔到人同情，只會令和理非發現原來你地真係只係想亂搞，而唔係有目的<br />\n<br />\n唔割勇武<br />\n只係有啲人真係唔用腦<br />\n係要死留搏比人拉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">求下你地走啦，今日夠架啦</span></span>"},{"pid":"a5afd3f77a55c55e8a6e7dfe176a01fc7b69a23b","tid":1484522,"uid":17024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:48:57.000Z","msg":"今日大家做得好好 走啦 求下你地"},{"pid":"93325394604554d4344fc219655c433bbed2a158","tid":1484522,"uid":17024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:49:07.000Z","msg":"今日大家做得好好 走啦 求下你地"},{"pid":"e702ca1c45c125788854d2831663912153434cbb","tid":1484522,"uid":17024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:49:37.000Z","msg":"今日大家做得好好 走啦 求下你地"},{"pid":"6587ee1b7203bd99a81e5023013c2155b4663820","tid":1484522,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:49:38.000Z","msg":"又唔係沖又唔係走其實做乜鳩<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1484400\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1484400</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"06db99c8c9650017048c28f992c078d7fcb54724","tid":1484522,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:49:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yZfU3Ex.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyZfU3Ex.png&h=f93dec4c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bKfBxxS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbKfBxxS.jpg&h=5e4ee816&